{"comments":"Pure Static Site Generation — Zero unsafeCoerce\n\nThis module provides SSG functionality using Hydrogen's pure Element type\ninstead of Halogen's HTML type. The entire rendering pipeline is safe.\n\n══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\nCOMPARISON WITH Hydrogen.SSG\n══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n\nHydrogen.SSG (Halogen path):\n  - Uses HH.HTML type from Halogen\n  - Renders via HTML.Renderer (contains unsafeCoerce at Halogen boundary)\n  - Compatible with existing Halogen components\n\nHydrogen.SSG.Pure (this module):\n  - Uses Element type from Hydrogen.Render.Element\n  - Renders via Target.Static (zero unsafeCoerce)\n  - Pure data all the way down\n\n══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n\nUsage:\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.SSG.Pure as SSG\nimport Hydrogen.Render.Element as E\n\nmyPage :: forall msg. Element msg\nmyPage = E.div_ [ E.class_ \"container\" ] [ E.text \"Hello\" ]\n\nhtml :: String\nhtml = SSG.renderPage defaultDocConfig defaultPageMeta myPage\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Configuration for the HTML document\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["lang",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["charsetValue",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["viewport",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["siteName",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["themeColor",{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Maybe"],"Maybe"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"]